===Are you a gourmet, (Trailblazer)?===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Acheron:''' Are you a gourmet, (Trailblazer)?
:{{DIcon|Warning}} <Grand Melodie Golden Hour>
:'''Acheron:''' Earlier, I helped this lady in Penacony without realizing she's actually a chef at a fancy restaurant. This is her restaurant
:'''Acheron:''' She'll be launching a special menu with a "peach" theme soon, and I highly recommend it
:{Choice} I'm definitely giving it a shot!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I'm definitely giving it a shot!
:{Choice} Aren't you coming?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Aren't you coming?
::'''Acheron:''' I've already tried it
:{Choice} Sounds "avant-garde"...
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Sounds "avant-garde," maybe something on the dark side of the cooking...
::'''Acheron:''' Dark side...? Does that mean there is a light side of the cooking as well?
:'''Acheron:''' Cooking... well, it brings back memories. I used to love it
:'''Acheron:''' However, it's hard to enjoy dishes when you can't really taste anything
:{Choice} Do you still cook now?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Do you still cook now?
:{Choice} Is this caused by the Nihility?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Is this caused by the Nihility?
::'''Acheron:''' Perhaps
:'''Acheron:''' Sometimes, I still cook up some food, but it's a shame that I can't taste much anymore
:'''Acheron:''' Still, there are some workarounds. For example, you can make ice cream out of snow
:'''Acheron:''' It's cool, moist, and creamy... a flavor that I'll never forget
:'''Acheron:''' I'll treat you to it when I get the chance
:'''Acheron:''' And don't forget to try the peach dishes too
:'''Acheron:''' [[File:Sticker PPG 13 Acheron 04.png|80px]]
}}
