===Oh, by the way,...===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Acheron:''' Oh, by the way, I came across something cute recently
:'''Acheron:''' As I was passing by the COLORS store, the store clerk asked for my autograph
:{Choice} You're famous now!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Well, you're totally a celebrity now with everything you've done!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' [[File:Sticker PPG 07 Pom-Pom 06.png|80px]]
::'''Acheron:''' It was all a misunderstanding
:{Choice} Was it a misunderstanding or...?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Was it a misunderstanding or something...?
::'''Acheron:''' Yes
:{Choice} Your autograph? I want one too!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Your autograph? I want one too!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' [[File:Sticker PPG 07 Pom-Pom 03.png|80px]]
::'''Acheron:''' It was all a misunderstanding
:'''Acheron:''' Miss Robin's makeup in the COLORS ad "Mien of Vesper" bears a resemblance to the attire of young girls from my hometown, leaving even me momentarily lost in nostalgia
:'''Acheron:''' And now that I think about it, I miss how those girls would worry about their makeup getting ruined in frequent thunderstorms
:'''Acheron:''' Oh, speaking of COLORS, I found some awesome products there, so I bought them as a small token of my appreciation
:'''Acheron:''' I think Miss Himeko will love this rose-colored lipstick
:'''Acheron:''' And this "Spring Scenery" eyeshadow will be perfect for Miss March
:'''Acheron:''' Not only that, they have some hydrating and cleansing products that people are raving about
:{Choice} Thanks!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Thank you! I'll spread the word!
::'''Acheron:''' You're welcome.
:{Choice} Didn't expect you to know about makeup
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Didn't expect you to know so much about makeup
::'''Acheron:''' Took you by surprise, huh?
:'''Acheron:''' I'll mail them to you before I forget
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Your friend is offline
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Your friend is online
:'''Acheron:''' Oh, sorry
:'''Acheron:''' By the way, do you know where the post office is?
:{Choice} I knew it...
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I knew it...
:{Choice} Do you need my help?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Do you need my help?
:'''Acheron:''' Oh, found it
:'''Acheron:''' It's right behind me
}}
